svg.title: \begin{equation}\begin{aligned}P(汽车在A|打开C是羊) &= \frac{P(汽车在A)P(打开C是羊|汽车在A)}{P(打开C是羊)} \\&= \frac{P(汽车在A)P(打开C是羊|汽车在A)}{P(打开C是羊|汽车在A)P(汽车在A)+P(打开C是羊|汽车不在A)P(汽车不在A)} \\ &= \frac{\frac{1}{3}\cdot x\cdot\frac{1}{2}}{\frac{1}{3}\cdot x\cdot\frac{1}{2}+\frac{2}{3}\cdot y\cdot\frac{1}{2}} \\ &= \frac{1}{1+\frac{2y}{x}}\end{aligned}\end{equation}
